flowchart TD
    A[Launch / Welcome] --> B[Wallet Home Dashboard]

    %% DID + Wallet Setup
    B --> K[DID Management]
    K --> K1[Create DID]
    K --> K2[View DID Details]
    K --> B

    %% Credential Management
    B --> C[Credential List View]
    C --> D[Credential Detail View]
    D --> D1[View Claims / Metadata]
    D --> D2[Check Status: Valid/Expired/Revoked]
    D --> C

    %% Presentation + Verification
    D --> E[Present Credential]
    E --> F[Selective Disclosure]
    F --> F1[Choose Attributes to Share]
    F --> F2[Confirm Consent]
    F --> G[QR Presentation]
    G --> H[Verification Result]
    H --> H1[Valid: Access Granted]
    H --> H2[Invalid: Access Denied]
    H --> B

    %% Settings + Recovery
    B --> I[Wallet Settings]
    I --> J[Backup and Recovery]
    J --> J1[Create Encrypted Backup]
    J --> J2[Restore from Backup]
    J --> I
    I --> B
